<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.2.5">
<l>kōḻiyuṅ kūṭa luṅkōyil koṇṭa kōvala rēyop parkuṉ ṟamaṉṉa</l>
<l>pāḻiyan tōḷu mōrnāṉ kuṭaiyar paṇṭivar tammai yumkaṇ ṭaṟiyōm</l>
<l>vāḻiya rōvi varvaṇ ṇameṇṇil mākaṭal pōṉṟu ḷarkaiyil veyya,</l>
<l>vāḻiyoṉ ṟēnti yōrcaṅ kupaṟṟi yaccō voruva raḻaki yavā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is like the cowherder with palaces in Kōḻi and Kūṭal.</l>
<l>He has four fine arms, broad like boulders.</l>
<l rend="indent">We do not recognize seeing him before.</l>
<l>May he prosper! If we estimate his beauty, he is like a vast sea.</l>
<l>Bearing a fiery discus in one hand, clasping a conch [in the other],</l>
<l rend="indent">oh, the way that one is handsome!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
